      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey${action:Talk}<BR>Then get me Hobgoblin Gobfrey's Mutated Jewel from the <FONT color=#a82424>Church Ruins</FONT>, Vanruha's Mutated Jewel from the <FONT color=#a82424>Catacombs Hall</FONT>, Laren's Mutated Jewel from the <FONT color=#a82424>Dark Tower Magic Institute</FONT>, and Carrera's Mutated Jewel from the <FONT color=#a82424>Silent Monastery Main Hall</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
