      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey$<BR>There have been a series of reports about adventurers who have been injured because they have entered the Abyss regions without proper defensive preparations. I was just getting worried about your safety, so it's great to see you return safely like this.</html>]]></talk_question>
